 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Assistant Designer, Baby Knits, Polo Ralph Lauren 2,828 reviews New York, NY Ralph Lauren 2,828 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job Company Position Overview
 The Assistant Designer for Baby knits will assist in weekly functions/ tasks or project based work covering the baby knit department. 
 Essential Duties & Responsibilities
 Assist with research in the market as it pertains to product, trim and graphic/ techniques, Create inspiration boards 
 In collaboration with Concept team; receive direction, inspiration from Creative director to prepare for seasonal kick off 
 Create CADs as directed , prepare stats/ line sheets for board review and handoffs 
 Assist in the creation of design presentation to design leadership 
 Update sketches to match proto and bulk approvals 
 Upload sketches, color ways, detail sketches and layouts to PLM 
 Experience, Skills & Knowledge
 BA in Fashion or related field preferred 
 Design internship experience a plus 
 Proficiency in ADOBE Creative Suite such as AI, PS, Indesign , XD 
 3D design proficency a plus 
 Ability to work with sense of urgency 
 Affinity and passion for the RL brand and children's apparel 
